{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji30.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给胡南浦的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给胡南浦的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年4月17日）南浦兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月十四日惠书敬悉，深感厚意。望仍在原地经营旅业，不必来京。谨此奉复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并致敬礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四月十七日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]胡南浦（1881—1953），湖南韶山市韶山乡韶源村人，毛泽东的私垫同学。当时在云南经营旅店，1952年返回韶山居住。1951年11月19日，毛泽东曾为其搬家赠送人民币500万元（折合1955年3月1日起发行的新人民币500元）。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":4,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":244,"page_end":244},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}